      "It pains me to say this because I want to keep Leon all to myself, but I cannot recommend him enough. A calm, composed influence within the team, bringing structure to the UX design process, and the end product — what can I say. There's no hipster, trendy stuff here; this is solid, well thought out design where everything serves a purpose.",
